sabotage.

120
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:34,630
But it wasn't an explosion, was it?

121
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:36,090
It was a disappearance.

122
00:05:36,090 --> 00:05:39,360
In all probability, they were
swallowed by a Sea of Dirac,

123
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,000
just like Unit 01 was.

124
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,200
And the restored S2 engine?

125
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,600
Gone, along with our hopes.

126
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:48,610
It's all because we're being forced
to use things we don't understand.

127
00:05:48,610 --> 00:05:50,540
<i>Things like the Evas.</i>

128
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:54,680
What'll we do with Unit 03?

129
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,820
We'll receive it here.

130
00:05:56,820 --> 00:06:00,220
The U.S. Government doesn't want
to lose the First Branch as well.

131
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:05,160
Didn't they insist on the right to
build Units 03 and 04?

132
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,830
And now they're foisting
it off on us?

133
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,460
They're really pushing their luck.

134
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:13,060
After a disaster like that, anyone
would get nervous.

135
00:06:13,060 --> 00:06:15,200
And how are you going to
do the test activation?

136
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,070
Will you use Rei's dummy plug?

137
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,390
I'll have to make a decision.

138
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:23,440
This is the dummy plug prototype.

139
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:25,710
Rei's personal data has
been loaded into it,

140
00:06:25,710 --> 00:06:29,680
but it's not really possible to
digitize a human mind and soul.

141
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,480
A fake, that's all it is.

142
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,420
It copies a pilot's thinking
process.

143
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:36,220
In the end, it's only a machine.

144
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:38,960
It transmits a signal
pattern to Eva,

145
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:43,460
and Eva believes there's a pilot
and synchronizes. That's enough.

146
00:06:43,460 --> 00:06:46,260
Load the data into Unit 01
and Unit 02.

147
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:48,530
There are still some
problems with it.

148
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:51,170
That's not important. As long as
the Eva activates, it's sufficient.

149
00:06:51,170 --> 00:06:52,660
Understood.

150
00:06:54,710 --> 00:06:57,810
I've delegated the transportation
of the Unit to the U.N.

151
00:06:57,810 --> 00:07:00,110
It will arrive by the end
of the weekend.

152
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:02,180
You'll take care of it from there.

153
00:07:02,180 --> 00:07:03,250
Yes, Sir.

154
00:07:03,250 --> 00:07:06,720
We'll perform the modifications
and activation test in Matsushiro.

155
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,120
And the test pilot will be...

156
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,120
Use of the Dummy Plug is not
recommended at this time.

157
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,820
One of our prospective
candidates...

158
00:07:11,820 --> 00:07:13,590
Will be chosen as the
Fourth Child?

159
00:07:13,590 --> 00:07:18,260
Yes, there is one child whose core
can be prepared immediately.

160
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:19,360
Then, I'll trust you to make it so.

161
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,850
Yes, Sir.

162
