Just yesterday.

179
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:21,260
But I haven't received a report
from the Marduk Institute yet.

180
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:24,020
The official documents will be
delivered tomorrow.

181
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:30,770
Dr. Akagi, are you hiding
something from me again?

182
00:08:30,770 --> 00:08:32,240
No, nothing at all.

183
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:35,600
Well, okay. So, who's the kid?

184
00:08:41,610 --> 00:08:44,050
Jeez! It's HIM?!

185
00:08:44,050 --> 00:08:45,480
It can't be helped.

186
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:48,020
All the possible candidates were
gathered together for protection.

187
00:08:48,020 --> 00:08:50,590
It's so hard to tell them.

188
00:08:50,590 --> 00:08:54,390
Asuka will be fine. Her pride
keeps her piloting her Eva.

189
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:56,800
Rei is exceptional,

190
00:08:56,800 --> 00:09:00,600
with no problems with her
Eva or our work.

191
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:04,340
Shinji probably knows the most
about the down side.

192
00:09:04,340 --> 00:09:06,960
I don't want him to suffer
any more hardships.

193
00:09:07,540 --> 00:09:10,770
But we need children of this kind,

194
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,980
in order for us all to survive.

195
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:16,640
Are you saying not to
complicate the issue?

196
