222
00:11:22,810 --> 00:11:25,240
Come to think of it,
you've changed.

223
00:11:26,110 --> 00:11:27,110
What?

224
00:11:27,110 --> 00:11:28,580
You, Shinji.

225
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:35,280
The first time I saw you, I really
thought you were a jerk.

226
00:11:35,950 --> 00:11:38,860
You didn't seem like you would do
something for someone else.

227
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:43,660
I guess you're just
really reserved.

228
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,070
Excuse us!

229
