I'm sorry.

233
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,420
I took it upon myself
to clean up a little.

234
00:12:06,420 --> 00:12:08,010
But I didn't touch anything
except trash.

235
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,960
Thank you.

236
00:12:17,330 --> 00:12:21,790
Eva pilots are sure
weird all right.

237
00:12:30,010 --> 00:12:31,500
Thank you...

238
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:34,480
Words of gratitude.

239
